<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 10:07:10 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>特朗普复赛迫在眉睫，拜登将发表高风险演讲</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/biden-to-give-high-stakes-address-as-trump-rematch-looms/articleshow/108295679.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108295679.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国总统乔·拜登周四面临其政治生涯中最关键的时刻之一，他发表了国情咨文演讲，旨在让持怀疑态度的选民相信这位 81 岁的总统适合在 11 月的选举中击败唐纳德·特朗普。大多数情况下，向国会发表的年度演讲主要是仪式性的活动，但到了 2024 年，随着民主党人拜登试图克服人们对他的年龄、美国经济以及加沙和乌克兰战争日益增长的疑虑，赌注将变得巨大。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 09:31:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/biden-to-give-high-stakes-address-as-trump-rematch-looms/articleshow/108295679.cms</guid></item><item><title>西班牙因隐私问题暂停世界币加密项目</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/spain-halts-worldcoin-crypto-project-over-privacy-concerns/articleshow/108289417.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108289417.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;出于隐私问题，西班牙政府数据保护机构（AEPD）命令 Worldcoin 暂停活动三个月。已提出有关信息和数据保护不足的投诉。肯尼亚、德国和法国的监管机构也在调查世界币的运营情况。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 06:48:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/spain-halts-worldcoin-crypto-project-over-privacy-concerns/articleshow/108289417.cms</guid></item><item><title>中方对台强硬言论是否会转化为行动？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/will-chinas-tough-talk-on-taiwan-translate-into-action/articleshow/108288645.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108288645.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国全国人大年度会议开幕，聚焦坚定推进祖国统一大业。国防预算增加。中国对台湾使用灰色地带策略。李总理省略了“和平”统一。国际社会对台湾的支持是对中国的干扰。华盛顿反对夺取台湾。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 06:25:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/will-chinas-tough-talk-on-taiwan-translate-into-action/articleshow/108288645.cms</guid></item><item><title>可怕的发动机起火迫使联合航班中止行程，返回休斯敦</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/terrifying-engine-fire-forces-united-flight-to-abort-trip-return-to-houston/articleshow/108288292.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108288292.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周一，联合航空公司的一架波音飞机在起飞后不久，由于其中一个发动机喷出火焰，被迫紧急降落在德克萨斯州。令人震惊的镜头显示，飞机左翼下方广泛散发出鲜艳的橙色火花，距离乘客的观察窗非常近，令人震惊。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 06:13:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/terrifying-engine-fire-forces-united-flight-to-abort-trip-return-to-houston/articleshow/108288292.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国指责美国在关系改善的情况下设计打压中国的策略</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-accuses-us-of-devising-tactics-to-suppress-china-despite-improvement-in-relations/articleshow/108287981.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108287981.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国外交部长王毅批评美国打压中国崛起并将中国企业列入制裁名单。他质疑美国作为大国的信誉和信心。王提到了前外长被解职的事。此次全国人大会议并未涉及人事变动。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 05:59:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-accuses-us-of-devising-tactics-to-suppress-china-despite-improvement-in-relations/articleshow/108287981.cms</guid></item><item><title>唐纳德·特朗普挑战乔·拜登为美国总统大选进行辩论</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-challenges-joe-biden-to-debate-for-us-presidential-election/articleshow/108285547.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108285547.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在两人成为 11 月份美国总统大选的可能候选人后，唐纳德·特朗普向乔·拜登发起了一场辩论挑战。特朗普表达了讨论国家重大问题的重要性，并呼吁随时随地在他的“真相社交”平台上举行辩论。尽管他最初拒绝参加与民调较低的竞争对手的辩论，但他现在对民主党主办的辩论持开放态度。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 05:16:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-challenges-joe-biden-to-debate-for-us-presidential-election/articleshow/108285547.cms</guid></item><item><title>金正恩下令在美韩演习中加强战备</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/kim-jong-un-orders-heightened-war-readiness-amid-us-south-korean-drills/articleshow/108284617.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108284617.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据朝中社报道，金正恩视察了该国西部地区的一个军事基地，视察部队的野外训练，并下令“加强战备”。尽管该基地的位置尚未确定，但此次访问是为了响应美国和韩国军队在韩国举行的年度联合军事演习。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 04:39:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/kim-jong-un-orders-heightened-war-readiness-amid-us-south-korean-drills/articleshow/108284617.cms</guid></item><item><title>法院裁决引发轩然大波后，阿拉巴马州通过了体外受精保护法</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/alabama-passes-ivf-protection-law-after-uproar-over-court-ruling/articleshow/108285530.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108285530.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在生育诊所因阿拉巴马州最高法院的裁决而暂停手术后，阿拉巴马州州长签署了 SB159 法律，为 IVF 中胚胎死亡或损坏提供民事和刑事豁免。民主党总统乔·拜登批评了这一裁决。阿拉巴马大学伯明翰分校计划恢复试管受精治疗。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 04:44:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/alabama-passes-ivf-protection-law-after-uproar-over-court-ruling/articleshow/108285530.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国外长王毅称加沙战争是“文明的耻辱”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-fm-calls-war-in-gaza-a-disgrace-for-civilisation/articleshow/108284249.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108284249.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国外交部长王毅称以色列在加沙的战争是“文明的耻辱”，并重申北京要求“立即停火”。自去年10月以色列与哈马斯之间的战争爆发以来，北京一直呼吁立即停火。自去年10月以色列与哈马斯之间的战争爆发以来，北京一直呼吁立即停火。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 03:55:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-fm-calls-war-in-gaza-a-disgrace-for-civilisation/articleshow/108284249.cms</guid></item><item><title>外交部长称中国将向联合国提交人工智能决议草案</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-to-submit-draft-resolution-on-ai-to-un-foreign-minister-says/articleshow/108284197.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108284197.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;王在年度人大会议期间的新闻发布会上表示，中国同等重视人工智能的发展和安全。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 03:53:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-to-submit-draft-resolution-on-ai-to-un-foreign-minister-says/articleshow/108284197.cms</guid></item><item><title>散货船被也门导弹击中，船员称三人死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/bulk-carrier-hit-by-missile-from-yemen-crew-says-three-killed/articleshow/108284134.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108284134.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国军方表示，也门胡塞叛军周三发射的一枚导弹击中了亚丁湾的一艘散货船，船员报告称，三人死亡，至少四人受伤。胡塞武装于11月开始袭击亚丁湾和红海的船只，他们称此次行动旨在表达对加沙巴勒斯坦人的声援。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 03:50:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/bulk-carrier-hit-by-missile-from-yemen-crew-says-three-killed/articleshow/108284134.cms</guid></item><item><title>策划终结中央情报局和联邦调查局的狂热分子在美国被判无期徒刑</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/fanatics-who-plotted-end-of-cia-fbi-given-life-sentences-in-us/articleshow/108283164.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108283164.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周三，一名美国法官判处四名成年人无期徒刑，他们经营着一座戒备森严的大院，正在等待一名被绑架幼儿的复活，他们认为这可以帮助他们摆脱中央情报局、联邦调查局和美国军方的威胁。声明称：“该组织打算利用这个孩子作为一项计划的支柱，以清除世界上据称腐败的机构，包括联邦调查局、中央情报局和美国军方，并杀死那些不皈依并追随勒维尔的人。”</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 03:18:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/fanatics-who-plotted-end-of-cia-fbi-given-life-sentences-in-us/articleshow/108283164.cms</guid></item><item><title>维护费用百万美元：美国为扣押的俄罗斯寡头超级游艇支付2000万美元</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/million-dollar-maintenance-us-coughs-up-20-million-for-seized-russian-oligarchs-superyacht/articleshow/108283224.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108283224.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国政府每月花费 100 万美元来维护一艘从俄罗斯寡头苏莱曼·克里莫夫 (Suleiman Kerimov) 制裁下没收的超级游艇。这艘游艇在斐济被扣押，其船主利用美国银行系统违反了美国制裁。根据法庭文件，圣地亚哥的联邦检察官正在寻求中间出售的授权。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 03:30:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/million-dollar-maintenance-us-coughs-up-20-million-for-seized-russian-oligarchs-superyacht/articleshow/108283224.cms</guid></item><item><title>防务报告称，中国加强灰色地带战以消耗台湾资源</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/china-steps-up-grey-zone-warfare-to-exhaust-taiwan-defence-report-says/articleshow/108283039.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108283039.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国使用气球、无人机和民用船只，强化了针对台湾的灰色地带战争。台湾正在采取各种措施应对威胁，包括增强基础设施的抵御能力、储存武器以及从冲突中吸取教训。北京还加强了金门群岛周围海警的巡逻。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 03:11:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/china-steps-up-grey-zone-warfare-to-exhaust-taiwan-defence-report-says/articleshow/108283039.cms</guid></item><item><title>刚果东部地区叛乱分子占领一座城镇，造成至少 10 人死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/at-least-10-people-killed-as-rebels-seize-a-town-in-congos-conflict-hit-eastern-region/articleshow/108282817.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108282817.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据称与卢旺达有联系的“3·23”运动叛乱分子占领了刚果东部的尼亚萨莱。袭击造成 10 人死亡。数千人流离失所，前往戈马。安全部队与叛乱分子作战。危机组织的理查德·蒙克里夫表示，暴力事件进一步恶化。刚果东部面临武装团体造成的人道主义危机。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 03:04:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/at-least-10-people-killed-as-rebels-seize-a-town-in-congos-conflict-hit-eastern-region/articleshow/108282817.cms</guid></item><item><title>外交部长：中国将成为全球“和平力量”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-will-be-global-force-for-peace-foreign-minister/articleshow/108282269.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108282269.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;外交部长王毅周四在北京举行的新闻发布会上表示，中国将成为全球和平与稳定的力量。王毅对记者表示，面对复杂动荡的国际环境，中国将坚持做世界和平的力量、稳定的力量、进步的力量。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 02:40:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-will-be-global-force-for-peace-foreign-minister/articleshow/108282269.cms</guid></item><item><title>捷克议会在该国历史上最严重的大规模枪击事件后加强枪支法</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/the-czech-parliament-toughens-gun-laws-after-the-worst-mass-shooting-in-the-countrys-history/articleshow/108282038.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108282038.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;捷克议会在该国历史上最严重的大规模杀戮之后批准了枪支法的修改，以收紧拥有武器的要求。该法律包括定期体检、报告可疑购买以及允许医生访问数据库的规定。当局可以预防性地从私人所有者手中没收武器。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 02:24:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/the-czech-parliament-toughens-gun-laws-after-the-worst-mass-shooting-in-the-countrys-history/articleshow/108282038.cms</guid></item><item><title>埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 排除在 2024 年白宫竞选中向特朗普或拜登捐款的可能性</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/elon-musk-rules-out-donating-to-trump-or-biden-in-2024-white-house-race/articleshow/108281564.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108281564.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 宣布，他不会为即将到来的美国总统选举中的任何一位主要候选人提供经济资助。这一声明是在他与前总统唐纳德·特朗普在佛罗里达州会面后不久发表的。尽管这样的会议可能会产生潜在的期望，但马斯克在其社交媒体平台 X 上发帖澄清：“非常明确的是，我不会向任何一位美国总统候选人捐款。”</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 01:52:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/elon-musk-rules-out-donating-to-trump-or-biden-in-2024-white-house-race/articleshow/108281564.cms</guid></item><item><title>加夫列尔·加西亚·马尔克斯想要毁掉他的最后一部小说。即将发布。</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/gabriel-garcia-marquez-wanted-to-destroy-his-last-novel-its-about-to-be-published-/articleshow/108281149.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108281149.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 00:56:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/gabriel-garcia-marquez-wanted-to-destroy-his-last-novel-its-about-to-be-published-/articleshow/108281149.cms</guid></item><item><title>胡塞武装在亚丁湾首次击中一艘船只，造成两人死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/2-die-in-first-fatal-hit-on-a-ship-in-gulf-of-aden-by-houthi-rebels/articleshow/108281066.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108281066.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 00:47:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/2-die-in-first-fatal-hit-on-a-ship-in-gulf-of-aden-by-houthi-rebels/articleshow/108281066.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>